      • removeNodeSelectionListener

        public void removeNodeSelectionListener​(NodeSelectionListener listener)
        Remove a node selection listener. Others may still remain after one is removed. An exception will occur if the listener does not exist.
        Parameters:
        listener - NodeSelectionListener to remove from the tree visualizer.

      • addRootNode

        public void addRootNode​(Node node)
        Add the root of a tree for drawing. Note that Node locations are dictated by Node.nodeLocation.
        Parameters:
        node - A root node whose tree we want to draw. Does not literally need to be a zero-depth tree root, just some node with children we want to draw.

      • clearRootNodes

        public void clearRootNodes()
        Remove all root nodes from the list to draw. Will result in no trees being drawn.
